Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.82,0:00:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire Style: Searing Migraine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.75,0:00:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even Fire Style?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.35,0:00:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Choji! Ino! You guys okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.93,0:00:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.25,0:00:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.54,0:01:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty good, just as I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.46,0:02:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakashi Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.11,0:02:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That being said,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.95,0:02:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've used four Lighting Blade shots\N{\i1}while using the Sharingan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.97,0:02:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't be sitting idly by.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They're using really good combos.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:02:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And here Kakashi Sensei definitely\Nnailed him with the Lightning Blade...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.60,0:03:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't he die?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I crushed his heart.\NHe really should be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But what I killed was one of the\N monsters that came out of his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We can assume that it died\Nin place of his real body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the same when he broke\Nmy Shadow Possession Shuriken Jutsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.56,0:03:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Something that looked like a heart was attached\N to his separated arm and it was moving on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What... does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If you include his real body,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,each monster that came out of his body\Nhas a heart, and they are all his.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,\Nit means he probably has five hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How can he...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.76,0:03:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,However, he lost one of them to\NSensei's Lightning Blade just now, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.48,0:03:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that means we have\Nto crush his other four hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to take him out completely?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.62,0:03:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're very perceptive.\NThat's exactly right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.52,0:04:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I took each of these hearts\Nfrom Shinobi I once fought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.48,0:04:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I can always replenish my stock... with your hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.21,0:04:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,By connecting his Chakra Network to the hearts,\N he incorporates their Chakra natures as well, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder he's able to\Nuse several different natures.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.66,0:04:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way,\N does the Hidden Leaf Village bury their dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.13,0:04:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Burials are a pain in the neck, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet Kakuzu's going to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,"We're going to dig up the body\Nand exchange him for money."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And here I thought I could have\Nsome fun with that bearded jerk...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.96,0:04:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He was nothing special, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.27,0:04:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're one to talk, especially since\Nyou got your head chopped off...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.64,0:04:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up. You keep quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you guys are intent\Non revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.06,0:04:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But you guys are too weak for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You all look like kids.\NI guess you were his students, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.02,0:05:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, with scum like him as your teacher,\Nyou won't amount to much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't insult Asuma Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Choji.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.73,0:05:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful loving bonds between\Nstudent and teacher, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, how stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.31,0:05:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You jerk...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Choji!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so great about an idiot like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.22,0:05:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Fatty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Choji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point of falling for such an obvious trick?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.46,0:06:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Choji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.85,0:07:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.12,0:07:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.63,0:08:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Little girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shikamaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.56,0:08:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You small fries.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.64,0:08:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.68,0:09:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.56,0:09:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,WATER
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.66,0:10:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How pathetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.26,0:10:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.35,0:10:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.73,0:10:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.19,0:10:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pathetic, man.\NWhat a disgrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.53,0:10:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too. How could you not realize\Nit was a Shadow Clone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh... You saw that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Shikamaru... How shall we fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's separate those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.46,0:11:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Our best plan would be to\Nattack them separately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,After we eliminate their ability\Nto do combo attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.74,0:11:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll focus on destroying\Nhis four remaining hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're going to do that,\Nwe'll need someone to stall Hidan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.29,0:11:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the most Chakra\Nstored up right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And I won't be of much use\Nin straight attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.44,0:11:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use my Mind Transfer Jutsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mind Transfer is a Combo Jutsu used after\N stopping an opponent with my Shadow Possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.83,0:11:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If you miss, you won't be able to return\N to your own body for several minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.23,0:11:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too risky!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.33,0:11:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.46,0:11:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- Huh?\N- What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.41,0:11:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll separate them after I restrain him\Nwith my Shadow Possession Jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.99,0:11:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But how do you plan on restraining him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.83,0:11:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll need a diversion, either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then {\i1}I'll{\i0} take care of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.83,0:12:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't do, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.11,0:12:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be finished if he attacks you\Nand gets even a little of your blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be just like before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.11,0:12:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be a bad move for us to\Napproach him and attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Choji.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.50,0:12:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You store up Chakra to take out\Nthe masked guy with Kakashi Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.36,0:12:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll capture him by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.03,0:12:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fulfill that role!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.89,0:12:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll capture him by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.56,0:12:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fulfill that role!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.76,0:13:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it. I'll leave it to you, Shikamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.06,0:13:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.13,0:13:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you that afraid of my powerful scythe?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.23,0:14:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm{\i0} your opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.25,0:14:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey-hey-hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.15,0:14:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sneaking around like that from a distance?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.10,0:15:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.07,0:15:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He picked it up...\N{\i1}and threw it with his shadow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't move in midair!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.89,0:15:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He's ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If I just focus on the shadow,\Na Jutsu like this is worthless!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.02,0:15:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not just sneaking around\Nfrom a distance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.44,0:16:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shadow Possession Jutsu\Nis a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You... asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Shikamaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.15,0:16:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.84,0:16:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.41,0:16:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a nice little walk... just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.86,0:16:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.37,0:16:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to separate me\Nfrom Kakuzu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:16:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You...jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.55,0:17:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't someone go with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.75,0:17:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really underestimating Hidan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And here that kid called Shikamaru\Nor whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.79,0:17:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,would've become a bounty\Nof high value someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.86,0:17:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.25,0:17:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But your decision was the right one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.28,0:17:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a great difference in battle experience\Nbetween you guys and myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.05,0:17:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing those headbands reminds me of the\N first Hidden Leaf Shinobi I ever fought...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.18,0:17:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The First Hokage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.01,0:17:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.23,0:17:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How old {\i1}is{\i0} this guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.99,0:18:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really immortal?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.02,0:18:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Something like that\Ndoesn't exist in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that I can keep on living...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I maintain a stock by taking\Nthe hearts of those I kill
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.78,0:18:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,before my own runs out of life...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.75,0:18:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So you won't let me get away, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This shadow technique...\Nonly lasts about five minutes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.32,0:18:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's just the two of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That works out well for me, too. You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.54,0:19:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Fire Style and Wind Style masks?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.89,0:20:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can stock five hearts including my own...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.39,0:20:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I will take your heart...\Nto replace the one you took from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.42,0:20:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I've waited for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.03,0:20:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
